- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper provides computationally efficient algorithms for the group testing problem. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the paper deals with combinatorial problems related to detecting defective items from a large set. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is possible as group testing is a technique used in some machine learning applications. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also possible as the paper discusses the gap between upper and lower bounds for the group testing problem.
